Villain is loose-aggressive (100% VPIP, 50% PFR) with a 3-bet in the sample. I have A-T offsuit from the SB — a strong hand. Against a LAG who plays every hand, I want to raise for value and charge them to see a flop.

A raise to 6 (3x BB) is a standard, clean sizing here.

